Please visit our directory of member National Societies at http://www.ifrc.org/en/who-we-are/directory/&#xd;
&#xd;
The directory provides addresses and contact information for the 189 National Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies who are members of the International Federation of Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies, and for those Societies who are in formation and invited as observers to the International Federation's General Assembly.
